  %section
    %h2 Summary
    :markdown
      ### HTML

      Speficies the architectural elements needed (a frame, fabric, etc)

      ### CSS

      Says how to arrange the HTML (how big to cut the fabric, how to attach it
      to the frame, etc)

      ### JavaScript

      Says how the page behaves ("when a user clicks this, do such-and-such")

